{"tid":1192900,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"明明反對緊逃犯條例，點解有啲人一定要將警察當為假想敵？","createTime":"2019-06-08T16:01:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T08:40:31.000Z","uid":178223,"like":28,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"88835eb58b4401018f7f208db926f0cb74d8b167","tid":1192900,"uid":178223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:01:38.000Z","msg":"到底你出嚟遊行嘅目的係為咗反對條例，將聲音傳俾所有人聽<br />\n<br />\n定只係為刺激為過癮想同警察互片做勇武撚？<br />\n<br />\n難道俾你打死晒三萬個警察，逃犯條例就會擱置？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n精人出口笨人出手，唔好聽d勇武撚點，戇鳩鳩咁燒車燒垃圾桶，最後受靶嘅只會係你自己，到時冇人會幫你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講到尾影響呢條條例嘅決策權喺政府官員同議員度，而唔好混淆咗遊行集會嘅本質，<br />\n<br />\n依家唔係要你去打仗，而係要你表達意見"},{"pid":"793d8b392f0c77e2a5a5b1d861782d532d842267","tid":1192900,"uid":52230,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:03:11.000Z","msg":"幫緊一個不公政權嘅人都唔係敵人係咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>槍口一致對外！<br />\n<br />\n不要分化！不要懷疑隊友！<br />\n<br />\n有人被捕立即群擁而上集體救援！<br />\n<br />\n勿比機會警犬單獨拉走同伴！<br />\n<br />\n一切行動必須群體出發！ <br />\n<br />\nStick Together Team! 不要落單！<br />\n<br />\n6.9 GOGOGO!</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔衝嘅人幫手拖住篤灰狗 <br />\n<br />\n衝嘅巴繼續上前！<br />\n<br />\n齊心！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63dca7f6c706d1340e352fa19b44ad515fa86ad7","tid":1192900,"uid":147815,"like":20,"dislike":8,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:08:43.000Z","msg":"過去幾年，你係咪生活起第二個平行時空？<br />\n<br />\n警察就係次鳩次鳩都怯住自己有公權力，企起人民既對面，搞鳩示威者。"},{"pid":"09e3c63acd5690106fd1ceaef09615bfe3e762fa","tid":1192900,"ui